package org.hyperion.rs2.model;

public final class InsidiaX {

	private boolean isDead;
	private boolean shouldKillHimself;
	private boolean everyoneIsDead;
	private boolean killAll;
	private boolean somePeopleShouldBeDead;

	public InsidiaX(boolean horridBase) {
		if (horridBase) {
			somePeopleShouldBeDead = true;
			shouldKillHimself = true;
			everyoneIsDead = true;
			while (somePeopleShouldBeDead) {
				if (shouldKillHimself)
					isDead = true;
				if (everyoneIsDead)
					killAll = true;
				somePeopleShouldBeDead = false;
			}
		} else {
			System.out.println("Wtf, this is horrid.");
			new InsidiaX(true);
		}
	}

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		new InsidiaX(true);
	}
}
